                     <interp inst="t18250217-147-person831" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I found 11 s. 4 1/2 d. on her person.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I throw myself on the mercy of the Court.</p>
